  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nUsing `pragma experimental ABIEncoderV2;` works when running `truffle compile`, but when running `truffle test` it doesn't (Syntax Error).\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nCreate any contract and add `pragma experimental ABIEncoderV2` after `pragma solidity...`. Then run `truffle test`.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nIt should run the tests with no errors.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n```\r\nSyntaxError: Expected \"solidity\", comment, end of line, or whitespace but \"e\" found. Line: 2, Column: 8\r\n    at peg$buildStructuredError (/home/vdrg/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:293559:12)\r\n    at Object.peg$parse [as parse] (/home/vdrg/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:306145:11)\r\n    at Object.parse (/home/vdrg/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:306198:23)\r\n    at /home/vdrg/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:203866:32\r\n    at FSReqWrap.readFileAfterClose [as oncomplete] (fs.js:528:3)\r\n```\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Arch Linux\r\n* Truffle version: 4.0.4\r\n* Ethereum client: integrated truffle client\r\n* node version: 9.4.0\r\n* npm version: 5.6.0\r\n",
